==Discussion Page==
[[File:DiscussionPageHighlighted.webp|thumb|A link to the Discussion Tab is present on the top left of every page.]]
Each page also has a discussion page, which is used to talk about contents of a page.
Please make a new header for each subject with a title and with what you would like to discuss.
When you finish writing a post, add <code><nowiki>~~~~</nowiki></code> right after it . This will automatically add your username and timestamp at the end of a paragraph.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Example:<br>
<code>==New Discussion Topic==</code><br>
<code>Text discussing  something. --Another User (talk) 00:00, 22 June 2024 (UTC)</code><br>
<code>: your reply to the Discussion Topic. <nowiki>~~~~</nowiki></code>
</div>